PrecisEnactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 41 - which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding in NEW BRUNSWICK between September 21 and September 23, 1999 to be of concern to the federal government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in respect thereof.

precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 41 -
which (a) DECLARES the severe flooding in NEW BRUNSWICK between
September 21 and September 23, 1999 to be of concern to the federal
government, and (b) AUTHORIZES the provision of financial assistance in
respect thereof.
